@startuml Analytics_Reporting

title Analytics Dashboard and Reporting - Activity Diagram

|User|
start
:Login to Platform;
:Navigate to Dashboard;

|System|
:Load Role-Based Dashboard;
:Generate Visualizations;

note right
  Chart Types Used:
  - Line charts (trends over time)
  - Bar graphs (severity distribution)
  - Pie charts (vulnerability types)
  - Area charts (cumulative data)
  - Heatmaps (activity patterns)
  - Candlestick (payment trends)
end note

|User|
:View Dashboard Metrics;

note right
  **Dashboard Metrics by Role:**
  
  Researcher:
  - Reports submitted, earnings, reputation
  
  Organization:
  - Programs, vulnerabilities, ROI
  
  Triage Specialist:
  - Queue: 12 New, 8 In Review, 47 Today
  - Avg Response Time: 2.5h
  - Validation/Rejection rates
  - Severity breakdown (Critical/High/Medium/Low)
  - Reports by status (Validated/Rejected/In Progress)
  
  Admin:
  - Platform stats, users, revenue
end note

:Click "Generate Report";
:Select Report Type;

if (Report Type?) then (Standard)
  :Select Predefined Template;
  :Set Date Range;
else (Custom)
  :Select Metrics;
  :Configure Filters;
  :Choose Visualization Type;
  
  note right
    Available Charts:
    - Line (trends)
    - Bar (comparisons)
    - Pie (distribution)
    - Area (cumulative)
    - Scatter (correlation)
    - Heatmap (patterns)
  end note
  
  :Set Date Range;
endif

:Click "Generate";

|System|
:Validate Parameters;
:Query Database;
:Aggregate Data;
:Apply Filters;
:Calculate Metrics;
:Render Charts/Graphs;

if (Large Dataset?) then (yes)
  :Queue Background Job;
  
  |Celery Worker|
  :Process Report Generation;
  :Generate Charts;
  :Create PDF;
  :Upload to MinIO;
  
  |System|
  :Send Completion Email;
  
  |User|
  :Receive Email;
  :Download Report;
else (no)
  :Generate Report Instantly;
  :Render Visualizations;
  
  |User|
  :View Interactive Report;
endif

:Select Export Format;

if (PDF Format?) then (yes)
  |System|
  :Generate PDF with Charts;
  :Download File;
  |User|
  :Save Report;
  stop
endif

if (Excel Format?) then (yes)
  |System|
  :Generate Excel with Data;
  :Download File;
  |User|
  :Save Report;
  stop
endif

if (CSV Format?) then (yes)
  |System|
  :Generate CSV (Raw Data);
  :Download File;
  |User|
  :Save Report;
  stop
endif

|System|
:Return JSON Data;
|User|
:Use API Response;
stop

@enduml
